ConfValue1: minimum fluorescence intensity value subtracted from the maximum fluorescence intensity value for sample 1 of test compound
DMSOMean1: Mean of the DMSO (vehicle) control for sample 1 calculated on a per plate basis
DMSOStddev1: Standard deviation of the DMSO (vehicle) control for sample 1 calculated on a per plate basis
EC80Mean1: Mean of the EC80 acetylcholine control for sample 1 calculated on a per plate basis
EC80Stddev1: Standard deviation of the EC80 acetylcholine control for sample 1 calculated on a per plate basis
ECMAXMean1: Mean of the ECMax acetylcholine control for sample 1 calculated on a per plate basis
ECMAXStddev1: Standard deviation of the ECMax acetylcholine control for sample 1 calculated on a per plate basis
Zprime_DMSO_EC80_1: Zprime for sample 1 calculated as 1-[3* (EC80Stddev1 + DMSOStddev1) / (EC80Mean1 - DMSOMean1)]
Zprime_DMSO_ECMAX_1: Zprime for sample 1 calculated as 1-[3* (ECMAXStddev1 + DMSOStddev1) / (ECMAXMean1 + DMSOMean1)]
ConfValue2: minimum fluorescence intensity value subtracted from the maximum fluorescence intensity value for sample 2 of test compound
DMSOMean2: Mean of the DMSO (vehicle) control for sample 2 calculated on a per plate basis
DMSOStddev2: Standard deviation of the DMSO (vehicle) control for sample 2 calculated on a per plate basis
EC80Mean2: Mean of the EC80 acetylcholine control for sample 2 calculated on a per plate basis
EC80Stddev2: Standard deviation of the EC80 acetylcholine control for sample 2 calculated on a per plate basis
ECMAXMean2: Mean of the ECMax acetylcholine control for sample 2 calculated on a per plate basis
ECMAXStddev2: Standard deviation of the ECMax acetylcholine control for sample 2 calculated on a per plate basis
Zprime_DMSO_EC80_2: Zprime for sample 2 calculated as 1-[3* (EC80Stddev2 + DMSOStddev2) / (EC80Mean2 + DMSOMean2)]
Zprime_DMSO_ECMAX_2: Zprime for sample 2 calculated as 1-[3* (ECMAXStddev2 + DMSOStddev2) / (ECMAXMean2 - DMSOMean2)]
